            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Nice infrastructure but under qualified staffs I can say. I visited to this school  on 20.03.2023 for my kids admission . My kid is 5 yrs old with Global cognitive delay though he understands and followed commands in English. I waited for an hour to meet to their newly appointed  special educator. Only discussing 5 mins she suggested to take my kid to psychiatrist and denied admission. As per govt. norms they can't deny admission. Anyways parents please vigilant and discuss all aspects before putting your kid in this school .  This is insane.",
          "publisher": {
